Bypass linkWe may be able to bypass the rate limiting by adding one of the following headers and change the IP per request.
Sometimes, we need to add multiple headers.
X-Forwarded: &lt;IP&gt; X-Forwarded-For: &lt;IP&gt; X-Forwarded-Host: &lt;IP&gt; X-Client-IP: &lt;IP&gt; X-Remote-IP: &lt;IP&gt; X-Remote-Addr: &lt;IP&gt; X-Host: &lt;IP&gt; X-Originating-IP: &lt;IP&gt;
